{"block1":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aging is a part of life that everyone must deal with. By reading this article, you will learn tips on how you can age gracefully and naturally. In fact, you&#39;ll see that you can control the aging process, and even slow down the signs of aging.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Don&#39;t worry so much about the number of years in your age. The actual number is less important than how your body feels, which&nbsp;is actually the true indicator of how old you are. You can feel young inside, even if your actual age indicates that you are a senior. The key is not to let your&nbsp;number of years&nbsp;dictate how you feel about yourself.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"\/images\/portrait-of-senior-activities.jpg\" class=\"img_right \" alt=\"portrait of senior activities\" style=\"float: right; padding: 8px; padding-right: 0;\" \/>&nbsp;Have fun doing activities that get you moving. You can slow down the effects of aging by continuing to enjoy the same activities that you loved in your youth. In order to get true fulfillment out of life you need to build positive relationships with your friends. These friendships will give your life energy, motivation and the love you need to make it through any day. A person is never too old to build new friendships. Do not hesitate to introduce yourself to new people and work towards building relationships that can sustain you for life.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aging skin is best concealed through a series of steps. First you need to apply your foundation and after that try a moisturizing concealer that is a shade or two lighter than the foundation. Putting on concealer after the foundation makes it easier to spot problems. Use your fingers or a brush to perfectly smooth the concealer over your skin.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Try not to fall. Many seniors are injured and sometimes even killed by falls. Take a 30 minute walk at least three times a week to <a href=\"nutritional-tips-for-a-healthier-happier-you\"  >help your health and happiness<\/a>. Keep your bones strong by lifting weights and getting enough calcium and <a href=\"http:\/\/www.webmd.com\/vitamins-supplements\/ingredientmono-929-vitamin%20d.aspx?activeingredientid=929\"  >Vitamin D<\/a>. This will reduce your chances of getting a fracture.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Try to spread joy wherever you are and whenever you are around people. Making others feel great and happy will, in turn, make you feel wonderful. Happiness is a gift that is worth so much, yet it is free to share.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Many people don&#39;t fully understand the aging process, and some even have trouble accepting the fact that they are growing old. Using the tips provided in this article, you will better understand how you can age gracefully and naturally. Applying these tips will prevent some of the negative effects of aging.<\/p>\r\n"}